<title>JERUSALEM, MY HAPPY HOME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jerusalem keimah In nuom,
 Kei dinga min deihum!
 Bangtik leh ka sepgim nusie'n,
 Lungmuong in ka um dem? (2)

[V2]
 2. Suongmantam kulh a um van In,
 Hukdamna kimna mun;
 Na sana kawtthel vak hawih chuh,
 Bangtik leh ka mu dem? (2)

[V3]
 3. Natna, gimtheihna leh thihna,
 Bangdin em ka lauh ding?
 Ka thil zing hi Kanaan gam hawih,
 Nitum lohna gam nuom. (2)

[V4]
 4. Sawlchak, Martar leh thiemgau haw,
 Hukdampa kimah um;
 Leichunga Krista mite hin,
 Amau chuh zawm tai tiu. (2)

[V5]
 5. Jerusalem, keimah In nuom,
 Lungin ka hun gulh hi;
 Ka sepgimna a beih tieng leh,
 Na nawpna chang ta'ng ka. (2)</lyrics>
</song>